{"tid":1287823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［保皇怕輸搞分化］三毛五毛全力攻打黃碧雲又失敗","createTime":"2019-07-05T11:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T09:26:28.000Z","uid":173849,"like":155,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"09743194e00e6f8f61b00504271bd8ccfbe126a5","tid":1287823,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:14:45.000Z","msg":"人地話開會過左非倒錢民生議案先<br />\n一堆五毛大做文章開post話佢係鬼<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">依家民建聯話義士係暴徒，搞到開唔到會<br />\n黃碧雲踢爆話開到，過民生議案先，有乜問題</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔想死士比人拉坐十年，唔通有錯？<br />\n佢幾時同義士割席左？<br />\n<br />\n民建議李慧琼轉軚支持暫緩修例，唔通李慧琼又係建制內鬼？<br />\n<br />\n黃碧雲612話612行動非暴動，咁快唔記得？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好彩分化post入面大部分回覆既巴絲都拆穿五毛奸計，呃到正評，呃唔到人心<br />\n<br />\n屌黃碧雲，邊個得益，自己諗</span></span>"},{"pid":"a78b4b464f8309d6f7f16f122605a0e853fea89e","tid":1287823,"uid":200758,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:17:51.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LvSJXSZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLvSJXSZ.png&h=0386e4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf96ac5cbd4981058ff5f5609168cd3d9e7a6c8a","tid":1287823,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T11:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07599bf6353363c0777132fd76a1a9d0b9b39176"